{"tid":2204034,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黃子悅等15人涉11.18救理大被困者被控暴動　轉介區院9月30日再訊","createTime":"2020-09-15T18:06:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T18:43:49.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ff181d709359afe60b760d81fc043708110a86d7","tid":2204034,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T18:06:08.000Z","msg":"去年11月中警方強攻香港理工大學，市民連日在油尖旺一帶前往校園，希望營救被困人士，最終逾千人被拘捕，其中11月18日在油麻地被捕的15人，包括前學民思潮發言人、立法會新界西參選人黃子悅被控以暴動罪。案件今日觀塘裁判法院再訊，控方申請轉介區域法院處理，獲得主任裁判官徐綺薇批准，將案件押後至9月30日早上9時半審理，被告可以原有條件保釋候審。<br />\n<br />\n控方今日修訂原有控罪，並且加控第七被告一項管有攻擊性武器罪。控罪指，15名被告，年齡介乎16至45歲，被控於2019年11月18日，在油麻地彌敦道的窩打老道、咸美頓街交界，與其他不知名人士參與暴動。第七被告蘇姓青年另被控於同日同地管有攻擊性武器，即為一枝鐳射筆。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2020-09-15/5377535\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.epochtimes.com%2Fnews%2F2020-09-15%2F5377535&d=%2F2JumwqaKkMO2nYek6mTvW5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=e99e952f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2020-09-15/5377535</a>"},{"pid":"70d3d7e1fad95ae82eee372f3e02112436dd9964","tid":2204034,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T18:11:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3406a48114944f08e4c1d2d3a4f64ebf28b778e7","tid":2204034,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T18:13:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"276abcd1f49a088ce66808be1f445327e301cb64","tid":2204034,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T18:15:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fac